---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import Breadcrumbs from "@/components/ui/Breadcrumbs.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="大崎商会について"
  description="大崎商会は個人クリエイター「おおさきくん」が運営。VRChat向け軽量アセット開発と居酒屋イベント「KemonoBarずんどこ」運営を両立。Quest対応・軽量化への徹底したこだわり。"
  keywords={["大崎商会", "おおさきくん", "VRChat クリエイター", "ワールドアセット", "Quest対応", "軽量化", "KemonoBar", "VRChat 開発者"]}
>
  <!-- Vision Section -->
  <Container>
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: "大崎商会について" }]} />
    <div class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-content-wrapper">
        <div class="hero-text-box">
          <h1 class="hero-title">
            大崎商会について
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-intro">
            みんなVRでたのしくくらそう！
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>

  <!-- Vision details -->
  <Container>
    <div class="vision-details-section">
      <div class="vision-details">
        <div class="vision-item">
          <Icon name="mdi:heart" class="vision-icon" />
          <p>軽くてリアルな食べ物で、みんなと笑いあえる時間を。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-item">
          <Icon name="mdi:chat" class="vision-icon" />
          <p>ちょっと会話が弾むような、日常に溶け込むアセットを。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-item">
          <Icon name="mdi:feather" class="vision-icon" />
          <p>使わなくても邪魔にならないほどの「軽さ」を。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>

  <Container>
    <!-- Activities -->
    <div class="activities-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">取り組んでいること</h2>
      <div class="activities-grid">
        <a href="/products" class="activity-card-link">
          <div class="activity-card">
            <div class="activity-icon">
              <Icon name="mdi:cube-outline" class="icon" />
            </div>
            <h3>ワールドアセット開発</h3>
            <p>居酒屋やバー、日常系ワールドで使える軽量な3Dモデルを制作しています。</p>
            <div class="activity-link">
              商品を見る
              <Icon name="mdi:arrow-right" class="arrow-icon" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/events" class="activity-card-link">
          <div class="activity-card">
            <div class="activity-icon">
              <Icon name="mdi:glass-mug-variant" class="icon" />
            </div>
            <h3>バーイベント運営</h3>
            <p>VRChatにて「KemonoBarずんどこ」を定期開催。交流の場を提供しています。</p>
            <div class="activity-link">
              イベントを見る
              <Icon name="mdi:arrow-right" class="arrow-icon" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="activity-icon">
            <Icon name="mdi:account-group" class="icon" />
          </div>
          <h3>コミュニティ支援</h3>
          <p>アセットの提供やイベントを通じて、VRコミュニティの活性化に貢献します。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Commitment -->
    <div class="commitment-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">大崎商会のこだわり</h2>
      <div class="commitment-grid">
        <div class="commitment-card quest">
          <div class="commitment-header">
            <Icon name="mdi:devices" class="commitment-icon" />
            <h3>Quest対応</h3>
          </div>
          <p>すべてのアセットはQuest単体環境で快適に動作するよう、徹底的に最適化しています。</p>
          <div class="commitment-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-value">100%</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Quest対応</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card light">
          <div class="commitment-header">
            <Icon name="mdi:weight-lifter" class="commitment-icon" />
            <h3>圧倒的な軽さ</h3>
          </div>
          <p>ポリゴン数やテクスチャを極限まで削ぎ落としつつ、見た目のリアルさを損なわない工夫を凝らしています。</p>
          <div class="commitment-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-value">低負荷</div>
              <div class="stat-label">ワールドに優しい</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card design">
          <div class="commitment-header">
            <Icon name="mdi:palette" class="commitment-icon" />
            <h3>実証済みの性能</h3>
          </div>
          <p>毎週のイベント「KemonoBarずんどこ」で実際に使用し、安定性と性能を常にチェックしています。</p>
          <div class="commitment-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-value">毎週</div>
              <div class="stat-label">実証テスト</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-detail-link">
        <a href="/about/technical" class="tech-link-card">
          <Icon name="mdi:cog" class="tech-link-icon" />
          <div class="tech-link-content">
            <h3>軽量化へのこだわり</h3>
            <p>大崎商会の技術的な取り組みを詳しく解説しています</p>
          </div>
          <Icon name="mdi:arrow-right" class="tech-arrow" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Owner Profile -->
    <div class="owner-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">おおさきくんについて</h2>
      <div class="owner-card">
        <div class="owner-avatar">
          <img src="/images/owner-face-new.webp" alt="おおさきくん" class="avatar-image" />
        </div>
        <div class="owner-info">
          <h3 class="owner-name">おおさきくん</h3>
          <div class="owner-roles">
            <span class="role">大崎商会主宰</span>
            <span class="role">個人クリエイター</span>
            <span class="role">KemonoBarずんどこ店長</span>
          </div>
          <p class="owner-bio">
            ワールドアセット開発とイベント運営を両立。「みんなVRでたのしくくらそう」をモットーに、Quest対応と軽量化にこだわったアセットを制作しています。
          </p>
          <div class="owner-links">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/osaki_shokai" class="social-link">
              <Icon name="mdi:twitter" class="social-icon" />
              Twitter
            </a>
            <a href="https://osaki-vrc.booth.pm/" class="social-link">
              <Icon name="mdi:store" class="social-icon" />
              Booth
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)), url('/images/about-bg.webp');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--main-color);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 400px;
  }

  .hero-content-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .hero-text-box {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--main-color);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--main-color);
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 0px white, -1px -1px 0px white, 1px -1px 0px white, -1px 1px 0px white;
  }

  .hero-intro {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--sub-color);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Vision Details Section */
  .vision-details-section {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }
  .vision-details { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .vision-item { background: white; border: 2px solid var(--main-color); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; text-align: center; color: var(--sub-color); font-weight: 700; }
  .vision-icon { width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem; color: var(--main-color); }
  .activities-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .activities-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
  
  .activity-card-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .activity-card { background: white; padding: 2.5rem; border: 2px solid var(--main-color); border-radius: 2rem; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .activity-card-link:hover .activity-card { transform: translateY(-8px); box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .activity-icon { width: 4rem; height: 4rem; background: var(--bg-color); color: var(--main-color); border-radius: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .icon { width: 2rem; height: 2rem; }
  .activity-card h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--sub-color); }
  .activity-card p { color: var(--sub-color); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; opacity: 0.9; }
  .activity-link { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; color: var(--main-color); font-weight: 900; }
  .commitment-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .commitment-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
  .commitment-card { background: white; padding: 2.5rem; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 2rem; }
  .commitment-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .commitment-icon { width: 2rem; height: 2rem; color: var(--main-color); }
  .commitment-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--sub-color); }
  .commitment-card p { color: var(--sub-color); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .stat-value { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--main-color); }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--sub-color); font-weight: 700; }
  .owner-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .owner-card { background: var(--bg-color); padding: 3rem; border-radius: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; border: 2px solid var(--main-color); }
  .owner-avatar {
    width: 12rem;
    height: 12rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 4px solid var(--main-color);
  }
  .avatar-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .owner-name { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--sub-color); }
  .owner-roles { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .role { background: white; padding: 0.25rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 900; border: 1px solid var(--main-color); color: var(--main-color); }
  .owner-bio { line-height: 1.8; color: var(--sub-color); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .social-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 3rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 900; color: var(--sub-color); border: 2px solid var(--main-color); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .social-link:hover { background: var(--main-color); color: white; }
  .social-icon { width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem; }
  
  /* Tech Detail Link */
  .tech-detail-link {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  
  .tech-link-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--main-color) 0%, #e67e22 100%);
    padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 3px solid var(--sub-color);
  }
  
  .tech-link-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }
  
  .tech-link-icon {
    width: 4rem;
    height: 4rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .tech-link-content {
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  .tech-link-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .tech-link-content p {
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.95;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .tech-arrow {
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .tech-link-card:hover .tech-arrow {
    transform: translateX(8px);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) { 
    .owner-card { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .tech-link-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .tech-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
    .tech-link-card:hover .tech-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg) translateX(8px);
    }
  }
</style>